      <p class="max-w-lg text-lg text-gray-600">
        Descubre cómo transformamos tus celebraciones en recuerdos inolvidables con un toque especial y mágico.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="https://wa.me/51908618955" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white transition duration-300 bg-pink-500 border border-transparent rounded-md hover:scale-105 hover:bg-pink-600">
          Contáctanos
        </a>
        <a href="/deco" class="items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-gray-700 transition duration-300 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md ihover:scale-105 nline-flex hover:scale-105 hover:border-pink-500">
          Ver Decoraciones
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex pt-4 space-x-4">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/tmcositas" class="text-pink-500 transition duration-300 hover:text-navy-900 hover:scale-105">
          <span class="sr-only">Facebook</span>
